<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Us - StreamAPI</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Email Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #ffffff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #334155 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .email-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grain" width="100" height="100" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="25" cy="25" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="75" cy="75" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="50" cy="10" r="0.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grain)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        
        .email-logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .logo-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-body {
            background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.8);
            padding: 50px 40px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .email-body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        
        .content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #3b82f6);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .message-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .message-details {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .message-details h3 {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .message-details p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .message-details strong {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px -5px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.6);
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3), transparent);
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .email-footer {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            color: #10b981;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .creator-link {
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .creator-link:hover {
            color: #059669;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .email-body {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .message-details {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="email-wrapper">
            <div class="email-header">
                <div class="email-logo">
                    <div class="logo-icon">‚ñ∂</div>
                    StreamAPI
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="email-body">
                <div class="content">
                    <h1 class="greeting">Thanks for Getting in Touch!</h1>
                    
                    <p class="message-text">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
                    
                    <p class="message-text">Thank you for contacting StreamAPI. We have received your message and our team will review it shortly. We typically respond to inquiries within 24-48 hours.</p>
                    
                    <div class="message-details">
                        <h3>üìß Your Message Details:</h3>
                        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= subject %></p>
                        <p><strong>Message:</strong><br><%= message %></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <p class="message-text">In the meantime, feel free to explore our platform for the latest movies and TV shows.</p>
                    
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="<%= siteUrl %>" class="button">üé¨ Visit StreamAPI</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    
                    <p class="message-text">If you have any other questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to reach out again.</p>
                    
                    <p class="message-text">Best regards,<br><strong>The StreamAPI Team</strong></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="email-footer">
                <div class="social-links">
                    <a href="#" title="GitHub">üì±</a>
                    <a href="#" title="Twitter">üê¶</a>
                    <a href="#" title="Discord">üí¨</a>
                    <a href="#" title="Instagram">üì∏</a>
                </div>
                
                <p class="footer-text">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> StreamAPI. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p class="footer-text">Created with üíö by <a href="https://github.com/BotCoder254" class="creator-link">@BotCoder254</a></p>
                
                <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.7;">
                    This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 